[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00520",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "こんな所で何をやってるんだい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00521",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "っ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00522",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "無数島群域にいたのに、\nわざわざランターナ大陸まで移動しちゃって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00523",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "いやあ、何を言ってるのかな？\n僕はただ夜の海を眺めようと思っただけだよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00524",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "こいつは驚いた。シトリンにしちゃ言い訳が下手すぎる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00525",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "お前さん……まさか、自分一人だけ\nヘル兄の命令に従おうとしてるんじゃないかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00526",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "イェルカが気が付いてくれてよかった。\n私、まだシトリンのこと、よく知らないから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00527",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……知らないのは僕のことだけじゃない。\nヘルトとゼロのこともだよ。特にヘルト！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00528",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "あいつらはやると言ったらやるんだ！\nその恐ろしさを知らないんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00529",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "だから、従うって？\nお前さんは本当にそれでいいのかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00530",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "やらなきゃ、僕が「管理」される側に回っちゃうだろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00531",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんた、もっと飄々としてた印象だけど……\nそれだけ追い詰められてるのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00532",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "僕からすれば二人がまだ呑気でいられるのが\n信じられないよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00533",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "嵐が来たら誰だって逃げ出す！　わざわざ荒れ狂う中に\n飛び込んだりなんてしない、それと同じなのに！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00534",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……かつてのアタシは世界中を飛び回ってて、\nあの二人と顔を合わせる機会も少なかったが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00535",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "どうやらシトリンはヘル兄に\n苦い思い出があるみたいだね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00536",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。付き合いが浅い私でも分かる。\n今のシトリンは怯えてる……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00537",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "シトリン、落ち着いて。力じゃなくて、\n話し合いで……知恵で解決する方法だってあるはずよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00538",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "だからそれが無駄で、呑気だって言ってるのさ！\n君は暴風と話し合いで仲良くなれるのかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00539",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……僕はヘルトの要求通り事を進める。\nそれが嫌なら力ずくで止めなよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00540",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "戦わずに済む話し合いってやつ……\nやっぱり、難しいわね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00541",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "我を忘れてるこの子には、一発お灸を据えて\nやる必要があるみたいだね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00542",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]